### List My Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/worker/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Review Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/worker/reviews/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{workerToken}}
Accept: application/json


### =========================================================================
### 💬 6. CHAT & NOTIFICATIONS
### =========================================================================

### List Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/chat/conversations?search[name]=Thợ
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Start Conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/chat/conversations/start
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "receiver_id": 2,
  "job_id": 1
}

### Get Messages in Conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Chào bạn, khi nào bạn có mặt?",
  "type": "text"
}

### Upload Media in Chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/chat/media
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/image.jpg
--boundary--

### Mark Conversation as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/chat/conversations/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### --- NOTIFICATIONS ---

### List Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/notifications?filters[is_read]=false
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Mark Notification as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Mark All as Read
PUT {{baseUrl}}/user/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Register Device Token (FCM)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/notifications/device-token
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "token": "fcm_token_example_123",
  "platform": "android"
}


### =========================================================================
### 🛡️ 7. ADMIN MODULE
### =========================================================================

### List Admin Accounts (Filters: status, search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/admins?filters[status]=active&search[name]=Admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

### Create New Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/admins
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Moderator A",
  "email": "mod_a@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role_id": 2
}

### Get Admin Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/admins/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Update Admin
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/admins/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Moderator A Updated"
}

### Toggle Admin Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/admins/1/toggle-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "inactive"
}

### Delete Admin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/admins/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### List Roles & Permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Role Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Role
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Moderator",
  "permissions": ["admins.view", "jobs.view"]
}

### Update Role
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Moderator Updated",
  "permissions": ["admins.view", "jobs.view", "jobs.resolve"]
}

### Delete Role
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get All Permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

