### =========================================================================
### 🔗 8. WEBHOOKS
### =========================================================================

### VNPay IPN (Webhook)
GET {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/payment/vnpay/ipn?vnp_Amount=1000000&vnp_BankCode=NCB&vnp_BankTranNo=VNP12345678&vnp_CardType=ATM&vnp_OrderInfo=Thanh+toan+don+hang+JOB001&vnp_PayDate=20260511140000&vnp_ResponseCode=00&vnp_TmnCode=VNPAY&vnp_TransactionNo=12345678&vnp_TransactionStatus=00&vnp_TxnRef=JOB001&vnp_SecureHash=abcdef123456
Accept: application/json
